INSERT INTO `interview` VALUES (1,'Morning Activities','eiken_25','\0','Recently, more people have started to make use of the early morning hours. These people study or do some exercise before going to school or work. Such morning activities refresh people and help them to keep early hours, so they are becoming popular. There are even special clubs or communities for morning activities now.','','2014-05-28 10:28:41','2020-03-23 06:44:32','\0'),(2,'Stamp Cards','eiken_20','\0','These days many shops provide various kinds of stamp cards to attract shoppers. Some of these are for discounts and others can be used to get free gifts. However, some customers complain that they get too many stamp cards wherever they shop. They think it is too troublesome to carry all the stamp cards and so give up the chance to use them.','One day, Tomoko and her father were checking out at the cashier at the supermarket.','2014-05-28 10:28:41','2020-03-23 06:44:32','\0'),(3,'Reading Newspapers','eiken_30','\0','There are many kinds of newspapers. Many people enjoy reading them before they go to work or school. People can get interesting and useful information, so they have fun when they read newspapers.','','2014-05-28 10:28:45','2020-03-23 06:44:32','\0'),(4,'Video Conferencing','eiken_20','\0','The Internet has given us some new ways of communicating. One of them is video conferencing, which enables us to have meetings with people in remote places. A camera is attached to the computer, so that the people you are talking to are shown on the display. Video conferencing is already used by many people and is expected to become even more popular.','One day, two office workers and their boss were talking about having a video conference.','2014-06-11 18:04:34','2020-03-23 06:44:32','\0'),(5,'Car Navigation Systems','eiken_25','\0','People usually take a map with them when they visit unfamiliar places. These days, however, many cars have navigation systems. These systems show drivers where they are and how to reach their destinations. Drivers can even hear directions from the systems, so they can drive safely and comfortably without looking at a map.','','2014-06-11 18:04:34','2020-03-23 06:44:32','\0'),(6,'Gardens','eiken_30','\0','People can do many things in the garden. Many people plant trees and flowers there, and some people like to grow vegetables or fruits. Having parties in the garden is also popular.','','2014-06-11 18:04:34','2020-03-23 06:44:32','\0'),(7,'Japanese Manga and Anime','eiken_20','\0','Westerners used to think it childish that adults read comic books on the train or at coffee shops in Japan. However, the art and uniqueness of Japanese “manga” and “anime” are gradually becoming better understood. As a result, more and more adults enjoy them in Western countries too. Some of them even wear the costumes of their favorite manga or anime characters.','One day, Mr. and Mrs Fujita were talking about Linda, who was coming from the United States the next week to stay with them. ','2014-06-16 13:17:43','2020-03-23 06:44:32','\0'),(8,'Shinkansen to Go Overseas','eiken_20','\0','The Shinkansen, or the Bullet Train, is expanding its network around Japan. Also, as the United States and Asian countries plan to develop high-speed railway networks, Japan is trying to sell the Shinkansen to those countries. In order to succeed in selling the Shinkansen, however, Japan has to beat the competing countries. Japan is advertising its high technology to beat the competition.','One day, Kenji and his father were talking about a new Shinkansen train.','2014-06-16 13:17:43','2020-03-23 06:44:32','\0'),(9,'Services for Pets','eiken_20','\0','Today, more and more pet owners treat their pets like real family members. As a result, the number of companies that offer services for pets, such as groomers, hotels, and funeral services, is also increasing. However, the cost and the quality of the services these companies offer greatly differ. Therefore we should be careful when we choose a pet service.','One day, Kohei and his father were looking at their dog anxiously.','2014-06-16 13:17:43','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(10,'Extra Lessons after School','eiken_25','\0','Today, some schools have extra lessons after school for the students who need them. College students and retired people support these lessons as volunteers. Sometimes the students work in groups and help each other, so they can understand their lessons better. This new way of learning is getting a lot of attention now.','','2014-06-16 13:17:43','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(11,'Remodeling Houses','eiken_25','\0','Today, many people choose to remodel their houses instead of building new ones. They can save money and reduce the waste of materials through recycling. People often watch TV programs which introduce skillful designers with new ideas, and this gives them a lot of information about remodeling. Remodeling houses may become more popular.','','2014-06-16 13:17:43','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(12,'Mother and Baby Groups','eiken_25','\0','Today, more and more mothers are forming mother and baby groups. In these groups, mothers share their experiences of raising children with other mothers. Also, many mothers can talk freely about their worries and troubles, so they find the mother and baby groups very helpful. There will be more such groups in the future.','','2014-06-16 13:17:43','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(13,'Festivals in Summer','eiken_30','\0','Many towns and cities in Japan have festivals in summer. People can watch many kinds of events, so they have a good time at summer festivals. Some people sing or dance with their friends.','','2014-06-16 13:17:43','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(14,'Watching Movies','eiken_30','\0','Watching movies is a popular hobby. Many people go to the video store to rent movies and watch them at home. Some people also like to see new movies in the theater.','','2014-06-16 13:17:43','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(15,'School Trips','eiken_30','\0','School trips are popular among Japanese students. Many students visit famous places in Japan, and some students go to other countries. Students travel with their friends and teachers, so they enjoy their school trips.','','2014-06-16 13:17:43','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(16,'English as the Official Language','eiken_20','\0','As economic globalization progresses, more and more Japanese companies are conducting business in foreign countries. Some of them have made English their official language. By doing so, they have made international business communications easier and attracted capable foreign workers. In these companies, all the documents are written in English and the employees have to speak in English at the meetings.','One day, Kotaro and his boss were talking about a meeting to be held in three months time.','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(17,'Rescue Robots','eiken_20','\0','Helping people who need to be rescued is not just work for humans. Today, special robots are being made for rescue operations, such as after an earthquake. These robots are built to be very strong, which enables them to go into dangerous places that people cannot approach. It is hoped that these robots will help to save many people in emergency situations.','One day, Takumi’s teacher was talking to the class.','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(18,'Cultural Courses for Elderly People','eiken_20','\0','Recently, the population of elderly citizens has been getting larger and larger. As a result, there is an increasing need for activities for them to do in their free time. So, many cultural courses in foreign languages, music, arts and exercises for the elderly are now available. These courses are designed to progress slowly so that older people can follow them easily.','One day, Linda got on a crowded train.','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(19,'Digital Music','eiken_20','\0','Music as a medium has evolved from analog records to compact discs. And today, many people buy music in digital form from Internet stores. They download the songs they have selected and enjoy them by playing them with computer software or copying them onto a portable player. In the meantime, CD sales have been decreasing recently, and many CD stores have gone out of business.','One day, Yuriko and her grandmother were talking about their favorite music in the living room.','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(20,'“Stop Idling” Campaign','eiken_20','\0','These days more and more people are interested in the “Stop Idling” campaign. It asks car drivers to turn off their engines while waiting at traffic signals or when parking even for a short time. If they do so, drivers can prevent their cars from emitting extra exhaust gas. This will decrease the amount of exhaust gas emissions and cause less damage to the environment.','One summer day, Mr. and Mrs. Takahashi were talking about the \"no idling campaign.\"','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(21,'Internship Programs','eiken_25','\0','Today, more and more companies are beginning internship programs. Students apply to the company of their choice and can actually work there for about two weeks. These students can learn about the company and the work itself, so they think an internship is very practical. Companies also welcome these students because they can contribute to society.','','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(22,'Growing Vegetables on Roofs','eiken_25','\0','Today, some people enjoy growing vegetables on the roofs of buildings. There are even member clubs for this where the members can take care of vegetables anytime they like. These members can ask the staff to look after their gardens when they are busy, and in this way, they can grow vegetables without difficulty.','','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(23,'Social Networking Services','eiken_25','\0','Recently, new services for communication have started on the Internet and it is becoming common. They are called social networking services. With these services, people can exchange opinions and information with each other, and this makes making new friends easier. Social networking services are drawing more and more attention as a new tool of communication.','','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(24,'Sea Travel','eiken_25','\0','Most people travel to foreign countries by air because it’s the fastest way. These days, however, sea travel is becoming more popular. There are many luxurious cruise ships that are of almost the same quality as high-class hotels. Travelers enjoy many activities on the ships, so they can relax and have fun.','','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(25,'A New Way of Learning Foreign Languages','eiken_25','\0','The Internet has changed the way of learning foreign languages. For example, people can talk to native speakers or have them correct mistakes through the Internet. As a result, they can learn foreign languages from native speakers at home. This way of learning has just started, but it will become popular in the future.','','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(26,'Computers','eiken_30','\0','Computers are useful in our everyday life. Many people have computers at home. They often use their computers when they write e-mails, and some people buy their favorite things on the Internet.','','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(27,'Fishing','eiken_30','\0','Many people like to go fishing. There are many good places for fishing in Japan, and some people try to catch big fish in the sea. Fishing in rivers and lakes is also popular.','','2014-06-24 13:06:37','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(28,'Camping','eiken_30','','In the summer, many people go camping. They enjoy walking around the mountains and cooking dinner with their family and friends. Some people go to rivers to swim or to enjoy fishing.','','2015-01-07 16:43:33','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(29,'Winter','eiken_30','','There are many ways to enjoy winter. Many people go out to the mountains to enjoy skiing and snowboarding, and some people stay at home and enjoy watching TV. Making snowmen is also popular.','','2015-01-07 16:43:33','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(30,'The Internet','eiken_30','','Today, using the Internet is quite popular. Many people use it to get information, and some listen to music on it. Chatting with others on the Internet is also very popular among teens.','','2015-01-07 16:43:33','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(31,'E-Books','eiken_25','','Recently people have started reading electronic books, which are also called E-Books. People can buy books on the Internet, and keep many of them on their E-Book readers or tablets. The users can change the size of letters shown on E-books, which helps old people who cannot see well. More and more people will use them in the near future.','','2015-01-07 16:43:33','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(32,'Charity Concerts','eiken_25','','There are various types of charity in the world. Sometimes concerts for charity are held to support those who are suffering from disease. Some famous singers or musicians hold charity concerts, and all donations are sent to sick people. These events give us a chance to help each other.','','2015-01-07 16:43:33','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(33,'Robot Cleaners','eiken_25','','Recently, more and more people have started introducing robot cleaners to their homes. These robots clean the floors of houses without the help of human hands. Using robot cleaners saves cleaning time and labor, and gives people more leisure time. The demand for robot cleaners will increase in the future. ','','2015-01-07 16:43:33','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(34,'Electronic Cigarettes','eiken_20','','Today, there are many people who need help to quit smoking, and various ways to support them have been introduced. For example, some smokers try “Electronic Cigarettes”, which are said to be healthier. These days, however, some experts report that Electronic Cigarettes could harm people. It is hoped that more research will be done to find other ways to help people to stop smoking in the future.','One day, Eri was talking with her father at home. ','2015-01-07 16:43:33','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(35,'Siestas in the Office','eiken_20','','Recently, more and more Japanese companies have been introducing office siestas. During office siestas, workers sleep for about 30 minutes after lunch every day. They allow workers to relax and get enough sleep, which is very important for them to work more efficiently and concentrate better. Thus, taking a rest and working for short periods at a time may be better than just working long hours.','One day, an office worker and his boss were talking about introducing siestas into their office.','2015-01-07 16:43:33','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(36,'Watching Movies from the Internet','eiken_20','','The Internet offers people many different kinds of content. For example, the Internet enables people who like movies to download and watch them anywhere. One problem is, however, that some people illegally download and watch movies without paying, which decreases the profits of the movie industry. In this way, the progress of the Internet has brought both good and bad results.','One day, Takashi broke his leg and stayed in hospital for more than a week.','2015-01-07 16:43:33','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(37,'Organic Vegetable Subscription','eiken_15','','This is a story about a woman who wanted to make a healthier life for her family.You have two minutes to narrate the story.','One day, a woman was eating breakfast with her husband.','2019-12-25 08:30:10','2020-03-23 06:44:33','\0'),(38,'Recruiting Workers at a New Factory ','eiken_15','','This is a story about a president who opened a new factory. You have two minutes to narrate the story.','One day, the president of a company was at a meeting with the sales manager.','2019-12-25 08:30:11','2020-03-23 06:44:34','\0'),(39,'Opening a Ski Shop','eiken_15','','This is a story about a couple that plans to run a store in a small town.You have two minutes to narrate the story.','One day, a woman saw a TV program about a skiing and snowboarding boom.','2019-12-25 08:30:11','2020-03-23 06:44:34','\0');
